    narr:generatedFrom "d1b09a828565de86" ;
    narr:narration """This hub gathers observations of an **authoritative register** running through aswritten's documents. The mechanics recur: predominantly [active, agent-first voice](narr:StyleObs_ActiveVoice), [short declarative verdicts with zero hedging](narr:StyleObs_DirectEvaluativeVoice), and [direct imperatives stated as settled fact](narr:StyleObs_DirectImperativeTone). Conviction is signaled typographically — [ALL-CAPS on key terms](narr:StyleObs_AllCapsEmphasis), [emphatic ALL-CAPS 'IS'](narr:StyleObs_AllCapsIS), and [bold markdown reserved for irreversible decisions](narr:StyleObs_BoldConviction). Authority is also earned through [precise quantification](narr:StyleObs_ConcreteQuantification) and [structured tables/bulleted decision lists](narr:StyleObs_TableTierStructure) that signal finality. A strong corrective strain appears: documents [open by correcting persistent errors](narr:StyleObs_FundraisingBriefReview_CorrectiveRegister) and [name the author's own prior conflations](narr:StyleObs_ConflatingProcessesRetraction). Idiolect markers (Matrix downloads, OS [bootloading metaphors](narr:StyleObs_6)) and high-conviction taglines like [the PE/the enterprise customer reframe](narr:StyleObs_PEAngleBiggerThanEnterpriseCustomer) and [the venture-money line](narr:StyleObs_CalibratedGrowth_ToneAuthoritative) recur. Notably the same authoritative register is attributed to [the customer's CTO](narr:StyleObs_CustomerCTOGuardPullRequests_Imperative), a design collaborator, a beta user from outside tech and Tony — not Scarlet alone.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_10> ;
